\":\"msg_0b9d221e02a7e6d6016a4ddbd83c4c8191aed929eabbecf827\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}}}}\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783487455755,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_dVmZPRX1z0ilN5dyk60LM3p5\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/SKILL.md\",\"offset\":241,\"limit\":320},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/SKILL.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n241:             \\\"intent_scores\\\": scores,\\n242:             \\\"load_level\\\": \\\"UNKNOWN_FALLBACK\\\",\\n243:             \\\"needs_disambiguation\\\": True,\\n244:             \\\"disambiguation_checklist\\\": UNKNOWN_FALLBACK_CHECKLIST,\\n245:             \\\"resources\\\": loaded,\\n246:         }\\n247: \\n248:     matched_intents = []\\n249:     for intent in intents:\\n250:         before_count = len(loaded)\\n251:         for relative_path in RESOURCE_MAP.get(intent, []):\\n252:             load_if_available(relative_path)\\n253:         if len(loaded) > before_count:\\n254:             matched_intents.append(intent)\\n255: \\n256:     text = _task_text(task)\\n257:     if any(keyword in text for keyword in LOADING_LEVELS[\\\"ON_DEMAND_KEYWORDS\\\"]):\\n258:         for relative_path in LOADING_LEVELS[\\\"ON_DEMAND\\\"]:\\n259:             load_if_available(relative_path)\\n260: \\n261:     result = {\\\"intents\\\": intents, \\\"intent_scores\\\": scores, \\\"resources\\\": loaded}\\n262:     if not matched_intents:\\n263:         result[\\\"notice\\\"] = f\\\"No knowledge base found for intent(s): {', '.join(intents)}\\\"\\n264:     return result\\n265: ```\\n266: \\n267: ---\\n268: \\n269: ## 3. HOW IT WORKS\\n270: \\n271: ### Invocation Contract\\n272: \\n273: This skill is invoked exclusively through `/deep:research:auto` or `/deep:research:confirm`. The command YAML owns state, dispatch, convergence, and synthesis.\\n274: \\n275: Never simulate the loop with ad hoc shell dispatch, nested... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783487455767,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_VaezKydSjgUWyLi4shKYx6H9\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/references/guides/quick_reference.md\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":240},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/references/guides/quick_reference.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: ---\\n2: title: Deep Research Quick Reference\\n3: description: One-page cheat sheet for the autonomous deep research loop.\\n4: trigger_phrases:\\n5:   - \\\"deep research quick reference\\\"\\n6:   - \\\"research loop cheat sheet\\\"\\n7:   - \\\"research iteration checklist\\\"\\n8:   - \\\"research loop troubleshooting\\\"\\n9:   - \\\"research tuning guide\\\"\\n10:   - \\\"research progress visualization\\\"\\n11: importance_tier: normal\\n12: contextType: general\\n13: version: 1.14.0.26\\n14: ---\\n15: \\n16: # Deep Research Quick Reference\\n17: \\n18: One-page operator cheat sheet for the autonomous deep research loop.\\n19: \\n20: ---\\n21: \\n22: ## 1. OVERVIEW\\n23: \\n24: Lookup surface during runs covering when to invoke the loop, what each phase produces, how convergence is computed, and where live state lives on disk. Defer to the full protocol and convergence references for deep reasoning.\\n25: \\n26: Operator contract source of truth for this page:\\n27: - command syntax: `.opencode/commands/deep/research.md`\\n28: - convergence stop contract: `references/convergence/convergence.md`, `references/convergence/convergence_signals.md`, and the deep-research YAML workflow\\n29: - state packet contract: `references/state/state_format.md`, `references/state/state_jsonl.md`, `references/state/state_outputs.md`, and `references/state/state_reducer_registry.md`\\n30: \\n31: ---\\n32: \\n33: ## 2. COMMANDS\\n34: \\n35... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783487455782,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"call_Wfc9t4Uvl5t470x4aZBbZSXL\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\".opencode/**/deep*research*.{md,yml,yaml,json,cjs,ts,js}\",\"path\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public\"},\"output\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/cli-opencode/manual_testing_playbook/04--agent-routing/deep-research-agent-iterations.md\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/agents/deep-research.md\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_research_confirm.yaml\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/assets/compiled/deep_research.contract.md\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_research_auto.yaml\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/assets/legacy/deep_research.body.md\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/z_archive/065-spec-kit-coco-sk-code-research/research/deep-research-strategy.md\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/z_archive/065-spec-kit-coco-sk-code-research/research/deep-research-config.json\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/