 Define the lifecycle contract for deep-research initialization, iteration, synthesis, save, reference-only dispatch concepts, and error handling.\\n27: \\n28: ### When to Use\\n29: \\n30: Load this reference when running or validating the research loop lifecycle. Use `../convergence/convergence.md` for STOP decisions and `../state/state_format.md` for packet file schemas.\\n31: \\n32: ### Core Principle\\n33: \\n34: The YAML workflow owns lifecycle orchestration, `@deep-research` executes LEAF iterations, and the reducer synchronizes packet state after each iteration and lifecycle tra... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783487455808,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_qygikeiYmMcCu9g0cztglmj0\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/references/state/state_format.md\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":240},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/references/state/state_format.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: ---\\n2: title: State Format Reference\\n3: description: Live state packet hub for the deep-research loop.\\n4: trigger_phrases:\\n5:   - \\\"research state format\\\"\\n6:   - \\\"research state packet hub\\\"\\n7:   - \\\"research file ownership model\\\"\\n8:   - \\\"research file protection rules\\\"\\n9:   - \\\"research packet location\\\"\\n10: importance_tier: important\\n11: contextType: implementation\\n12: version: 1.14.0.29\\n13: ---\\n14: \\n15: # State Format Reference\\n16: \\n17: Live state packet hub for deep-research files, mutability, and routed state references.\\n18: \\n19: ---\\n20: \\n21: ## 1. OVERVIEW\\n22: \\n23: ### Purpose\\n24: \\n25: Summarize the live deep-research packet files, mutability rules, and focused state references without carrying every JSON shape inline.\\n26: \\n27: ### When to Use\\n28: \\n29: Load this hub when navigating packet files, deciding file ownership, or choosing which detailed state reference to load next.\\n30: \\n31: ### Routed Details\\n32: \\n33: - `state_jsonl.md` for config, iteration, event, lifecycle, graph, and blocked-stop records.\\n34: - `state_outputs.md` for strategy, iteration markdown, `research.md`, dashboard, and resource-map output.\\n35: - `state_reducer_registry.md` for reducer ownership, findings registry, validation, reconstruction, and file protection.\\n36: \\n37: For iterative code review state, use `deep-review`. Review-mode state is not part of this ... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783487455819,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_gkXCvPN5xGGr983xp4HS28Ho\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/references/convergence/convergence.md\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":260},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/references/convergence/convergence.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: ---\\n2: title: Convergence Detection Reference\\n3: description: Live stop contract and navigation hub for deep-research convergence.\\n4: trigger_phrases:\\n5:   - \\\"research convergence detection\\\"\\n6:   - \\\"research stop contract\\\"\\n7:   - \\\"research stopreason values\\\"\\n8:   - \\\"research legal stop gates\\\"\\n9:   - \\\"research convergence decision order\\\"\\n10: importance_tier: important\\n11: contextType: implementation\\n12: version: 1.14.0.20\\n13: ---\\n14: \\n15: # Convergence Detection Reference\\n16: \\n17: Live stop-contract hub for deep-research convergence and routed convergence references.\\n18: \\n19: ---\\n20: \\n21: ## 1. OVERVIEW\\n22: \\n23: ### Purpose\\n24: \\n25: Keep the executable deep-research stop contract short enough to load during routing while pointing detailed signal, recovery, and graph behavior to focused references.\\n26: \\n27: ### When to Use\\n28: \\n29: Load this hub when deciding whether a deep-research loop should continue, recover, or stop.\\n30: \\n31: ### Key Sources\\n32: \\n33: - Command syntax: `.opencode/commands/deep/research.md`\\n34: - Workflow algorithm: `.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_research_auto.yaml` and `_confirm.yaml`\\n35: - Signal details: `references/convergence/convergence_signals.md`\\n36: - Recovery details: `references/convergence/convergence_recovery.md`\\n37: - Graph stop gates: `references/convergence/convergence_graph.md`\\n38:... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1783487456155,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f4022e398001iR77CJuF4olCnk\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"b7f98a4286df6763fa8ce91614585e54841d935c\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f4022a1fa001NwWNY7pQ8Z2e3c\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":40832,\"input\":15938,\"output\":423,\"reasoning\":407,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":24064}},\"cost\":0}}\n{\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1783487457404,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f4022e87a001T1SNCACnP4eKRw\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f4022e4cf0014U60owVaZ1xILn\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"snapshot\":\"b7f98a4286df6763fa8ce91614585e54841d935c\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}","truncated":true,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-9/logs/fanout-lineage.out","text":"{\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1783487367744,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f40218a3e00147THzm74xe76F8\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f4021702b001g0rw6v09D76TFK\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"snapshot\":\"17c839cd2ba4897d41c5983b94fafb30431e2ad1\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n{\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1783487378628,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f4021b1af001CJ5ZlpUQokI05K\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f4021702b001g0rw6v09D76TFK\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"SKILL ROUTING: User directed -> deep-research with cli-opencode executor. I’ll load the workflow contract first, then write only inside the supplied lineage artifact directory.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1783487377839,\"end\":1783487378627},\"metadata\":{\"openai\":{\"itemId\":\"msg_0cc9b5cdcf2a3e23016a4ddb91d71081919b3661929f7e9bcd\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}}}}\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783487423149,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"mk-spec-memory_memory_match_triggers\",\"callID\":\"call_a6na8RdCsLd0ftI3fxB7io9U\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"input\":{\"prompt\":\"You are orchestrating the deep-research workflow YAML as a detached fan-out lineage.\\nThis is an explicit parallel-detached OpenCode lineage, not a self-invocation of the parent session.\\nUse the separate lineage directory and session id below as the detached state boundary.\\n\\n\\nRead .opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/SKILL.md and execute the research loop with these parameters:\\n  spec_folder: .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research\\n  config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir: .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-9\\n  session_id: fanout-gpt55-fast-9-1783486518892-2qss01\\n  executor: cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast\\n  loop_type: research\\n  config.stopPolicy: convergence\\n  research_topic: Validate and stress-test the merge design for folding deep-loop-runtime into deep-loop-workflows as system-deep-loop: structural layout, bidirectional path-coupling repair, the system-spec-kit tooling-borrow, reference migration across commands/agents/READMEs/advisor-corpus, and whether fallback-router.ts should be wired for real GLM-5.2 to MiMo-v2.5-Pro fallback.\\n  config.maxIterations: 10\\nThe step_resolve_artifact_root step will bind artifact_dir to .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-9 via the\\nconfig.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir override — do NOT run the resolveArtifactRoot node\\ncommand; bind artifact_dir directly to the override value.\\n\\nRun phase_init, phase_main_loop (to legal convergence OR config.maxIterations, whichever comes first), and phase_synthesis.\\nWrite all outputs to .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-u... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1783487423491,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f402264000016Ht68Dw67HB8nf\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"744206c74582792fd745e916f3f6835ab5a4b840\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f4021702b001g0rw6v09D76TFK\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":32430,\"input\":31264,\"output\":650,\"reasoning\":516,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":0}},\"cost\":0}}\n{\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1783487424751,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f402268ed0016c2TSjyXtnyik0\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f40226536001l4LDfpl3u1KpAM\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"snapshot\":\"744206c74582792fd745e916f3f6835ab5a4b840\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783487438540,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"skill\",\"callID\":\"call_XkiPZThwzVIGgPxOniqDZPW8\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"name\":\"deep-research\"},\"output\":\"<skill_content name=\\\"deep-research\\\">\\n# Skill: deep-research\\n\\n<!-- Keywords: autoresearch, deep-research, iterative-research, autonomous-loop, convergence-detection, externalized-state, fresh-context, research-agent, JSONL-state, strategy-file -->\\n\\n# Autonomous Deep Research Loop\\n\\nNote: `Task` is allowed for the command executor that manages the loop. The `@deep-research` agent itself is LEAF-only and does not dispatch sub-agents.\\n\\nIterative research protocol with fresh context per iteration, externalized state, and convergence detection for deep technical investigation.\\n\\nRuntime path resolution:\\n- OpenCode/Copilot runtime: `.opencode/agents/*.md`\\n- Claude runtime: `.claude/agents/*.md`\\n\\nOperator contract precedence for this skill surface:\\n- Command entrypoint syntax in `.opencode/commands/deep/research.md`\\n- Convergence math in `references/convergence/convergence.md` and the deep-research YAML workflow\\n- Runtime agent inventories from the checked-in runtime directories above\\n\\n### Convergence Threshold Semantics\\n\\n**Default:** 0.05 on newInfoRatio (fully-new=1.0, partially-new=0.5, +0.10 simplicity bonus, capped 1.0)\\n\\n**Semantic:** `convergenceThreshold` compares newly discovered information against accumulated research knowledge with negative-knowledge emphasis. Lower = more iterations / higher signal threshold.\\n\\n**NOT INTERCHANGEABLE with siblings:**\\n- `deep-review` uses 0.10 default on weighted P0/P1/P2 severity ratio\\n- `deep-ai-council` uses 0.20 default on adjudicator-verdict stability\\n\\nCarrying threshold expectations across siblings will cause unexpected iteration counts. See this skill's changelog and decision records for the cross-sibling threshold research and parity invariants that confirm ... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783487438568,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_zyMqNjKtxqIMQsGVwtj9oHMA\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/SKILL.md\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":240},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/SKILL.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: ---\\n2: name: deep-research\\n3: description: \\\"Autonomous deep-research loop: iterative investigation, externalized state, convergence detection, fresh context per pass.\\\"\\n4: allowed-tools: [Read, Write, Edit, Bash, Grep, Glob, Task, WebFetch, memory_context, memory_search]\\n5: argument-hint: \\\"[topic] [:auto|:confirm] [--max-iterations=N] [--convergence=N]\\\"\\n6: version: 1.14.0.0\\n7: ---\\n8: \\n9: <!-- Keywords: autoresearch, deep-research, iterative-research, autonomous-loop, convergence-detection, externalized-state, fresh-context, research-agent, JSONL-state, strategy-file -->\\n10: \\n11: # Autonomous Deep Research Loop\\n12: \\n13: Note: `Task` is allowed for the command executor that manages the loop. The `@deep-research` agent itself is LEAF-only and does not dispatch sub-agents.\\n14: \\n15: Iterative research protocol with fresh context per iteration, externalized state, and convergence detection for deep technical investigation.\\n16: \\n17: Runtime path resolution:\\n18: - OpenCode/Copilot runtime: `.opencode/agents/*.md`\\n19: - Claude runtime: `.claude/agents/*.md`\\n20: \\n21: Operator contract precedence for this skill surface:\\n22: - Command entrypoint syntax in `.opencode/commands/deep/research.md`\\n23: - Convergence math in `references/convergence/convergence.md` and the deep-research YAML workflow\\n24: - Runtime agent inventories from the checked-in runtime directories above\\n25: \\n26: ### Convergence Threshold Seman... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783487438577,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_WCAIixslh741bLRcPOj460g0\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/cli-opencode/SKILL.md\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":200},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/cli-opencode/SKILL.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: ---\\n2: name: cli-opencode\\n3: description: \\\"OpenCode CLI orchestrator: external dispatch, in-OpenCode parallel sessions, cross-AI handback with full runtime context.\\\"\\n4: allowed-tools: [Bash, Read, Glob, Grep]\\n5: version: 1.3.15.1\\n6: hard_rules:\\n7:   - id: stdin-redirect-required\\n8:     check: stdin-redirect-required\\n9:     message: \\\"Ad-hoc `opencode run` MUST close/redirect stdin (`</dev/null`) — omitting it can hang indefinitely at 0% CPU with zero output.\\\"\\n10:     severity: warn\\n11:   - id: no-bare-agent-general\\n12:     check: no-bare-agent-general\\n13:     message: \\\"Never pass a bare top-level `--agent general`; opencode rejects it on run.\\\"\\n14:     severity: warn\\n15:   - id: command-flag-for-slash-prompt\\n16:     check: command-flag-for-slash-prompt\\n17:     message: \\\"A slash-command-shaped prompt (`/family:name ...`) needs `--command <family>/<name>`, else opencode silently delivers the slash text as raw prose.\\\"\\n18:     severity: warn\\n19:   - id: share-requires-confirmation\\n20:     check: share-requires-confirmation\\n21:     message: \\\"`--share` publishes the session and requires prior operator confirmation.\\\"\\n22:     severity: warn\\n23: ---\\n24: \\n25: <!-- Keywords: opencode, opencode-cli, opencode-run, cross-ai, spec-kit-runtime, plugin-runtime, parallel-sessions, share-url, detached-session, agent-delegation, deepseek, openai, minimax, minimax-coding-plan, minimax-m3, token-plan, xiaomi, xiaomi-token-plan, xiaomi-token-plan-ams, xiaom... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783487438597,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_TDfPFYZmLgjsjkFQgFibYoMM\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-9\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":200},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-9</path>\\n<type>directory</type>\\n<entries>\\n.executor-state/\\n\\n(1 entries)\\n</entries>\",\"metadata\":{\"preview\":\".executor-state/\",\"truncated\":false,\"loaded\":[],\"display\":{\"type\":\"directory\",\"path\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-9\",\"entries\":[\".executor-state/\"],\"offset\":1,\"totalEntries\":1,\"truncated\":false}},\"title\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-9\",\"time\":{\"start\":1783487438594,\"end\":1783487438596}},\"metadata\":{\"openai\":{\"itemId\":\"fc_0f08e067c747bc0e016a4ddbce79d08191accb582790731670\"}},\"id\":\"prt_f40229ef9001S8TzA7G1F4zUfi\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f40226536001l4LDfpl3u1KpAM\"}}\n{\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1783487439014,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f4022a0a3001Es6YIFl7F40xkp\",\"reason\":\"tool-