e truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783487455819,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_gkXCvPN5xGGr983xp4HS28Ho\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/references/convergence/convergence.md\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":260},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/references/convergence/convergence.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: ---\\n2: title: Convergence Detection Reference\\n3: description: Live stop contract and navigation hub for deep-research convergence.\\n4: trigger_phrases:\\n5:   - \\\"research convergence detection\\\"\\n6:   - \\\"research stop contract\\\"\\n7:   - \\\"research stopreason values\\\"\\n8:   - \\\"research legal stop gates\\\"\\n9:   - \\\"research convergence decision order\\\"\\n10: importance_tier: important\\n11: contextType: implementation\\n12: version: 1.14.0.20\\n13: ---\\n14: \\n15: # Convergence Detection Reference\\n16: \\n17: Live stop-contract hub for deep-research convergence and routed convergence references.\\n18: \\n19: ---\\n20: \\n21: ## 1. OVERVIEW\\n22: \\n23: ### Purpose\\n24: \\n25: Keep the executable deep-research stop contract short enough to load during routing while pointing detailed signal, recovery, and graph behavior to focused references.\\n26: \\n27: ### When to Use\\n28: \\n29: Load this hub when deciding whether a deep-research loop should continue, recover, or stop.\\n30: \\n31: ### Key Sources\\n32: \\n33: - Command syntax: `.opencode/commands/deep/research.md`\\n34: - Workflow algorithm: `.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_research_auto.yaml` and `_confirm.yaml`\\n35: - Signal details: `references/convergence/convergence_signals.md`\\n36: - Recovery details: `references/convergence/convergence_recovery.md`\\n37: - Graph stop gates: `references/convergence/convergence_graph.md`\\n38:... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1783487456155,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f4022e398001iR77CJuF4olCnk\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"b7f98a4286df6763fa8ce91614585e54841d935c\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f4022a1fa001NwWNY7pQ8Z2e3c\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":40832,\"input\":15938,\"output\":423,\"reasoning\":407,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":24064}},\"cost\":0}}\n{\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1783487457404,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f4022e87a001T1SNCACnP4eKRw\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f4022e4cf0014U60owVaZ1xILn\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"snapshot\":\"b7f98a4286df6763fa8ce91614585e54841d935c\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n{\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1783487470336,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f402303e4001fc8ESfbnZvWWrx\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f4022e4cf0014U60owVaZ1xILn\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I found the executable workflow assets under `.opencode/commands/deep/assets/`. I’m reading the YAML and state schemas now so the lineage files match the command-owned contract instead of inventing a format.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1783487464420,\"end\":1783487470334},\"metadata\":{\"openai\":{\"itemId\":\"msg_00cf37fcdd012819016a4ddbe86b448191abe8c3f85c238d5e\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}}}}\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1783487470375,\"sessionID\":\"ses_0bfde9160ffemveMH7ylOYjZ1V\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_4LLB8FThUFNLLsSl9DDfrbZY\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/comman